draughts.model

Enum GameType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GameType>
      • draughts.model.GameType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GameType>

    public enum GameType
extends java.lang.Enum<GameType>
    type : the type-number coding for the draughts game type.

    A valid GameType corresponding to the type encoding for type of draughts game:
    - INTERNATIONAL (20)
    - ENGLISH (21)
    - ITALIAN (22)
    - AMERICAN_POOL (23)
    - SPANISH (24)
    - RUSSIAN (25)
    - BRAZILIAN (26)
    - CANADIAN (27)
    - PORTUGUESE (28)
    - CZECH (29)
    - TURKISH (30)
    - THAI (31)
    - FRISIAN (40)
    - SPANTSIRETTI (41).

    Default return value is INTERNATIONAL (20).

    See Also:
    http://pdn.fmjd.org - gametype-section
